id: pm-github-2u31
title: "--dry-run silently wrote items instead of previewing"
description: "Flag registered as --dry-run but read as ctx.options['dry-run']; runtime normalizes to camelCase 'dryRun', so dry-run was always false and the importer created real items in 'preview' mode. Fixed by reading both key forms via optionEnabled()."
